title: Conquest for Global Domination (+tharhalas+)
description:
Tharhalas Presents:
         ===================== 

Conquest for Global Domination v1.0
        Â©1989  Mark C. Bayless

    The classic text game for world      
      domination you played on your       
      computer over 25 years ago is       
      ready for you to rediscover all      
                  over again!                
                              
      It took me years to track down      
  this game, and I'm glad I finally was 
     able to locate it, as not only is     
  this a game I loved way back when,   
     it's yet another piece of gaming    
     history from the shareware era  
      that might have been lost to    
                     time.   

    Help preserve these older games, 
  share what you find on an old floppy,  
  on an old BBS backup,(huh - there's
     got to be a BBS out there still
   somewhere..?  If you know of one,
     let me know, please, especially
            any in Oregon!), etc.     
 

--->       Play with DOSBox
